---
// Hero.astro
---

<section id="hero" class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content reveal">
            <h1 class="hero-title"><span class="hero-greeting">Hi, I'm</span> <span
                    class="highlight text-gradient">Rakibul Hasan Rizvi</span></h1>
            <h2 class="hero-subtitle">Systems Engineer | Linux Administrator | <span class="text-gradient">DevOps
                    Enthusiast</span></h2>
            <p class="hero-desc">I am a Systems Engineer specializing in Linux server administration, VoIP systems, and
                cloud infrastructure. I have hands-on experience managing production systems including IPPBX platforms,
                email servers, and virtualization environments. I am currently expanding my expertise in DevOps,
                automation, and cloud technologies.</p>
            <div class="hero-cta">
                <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">View My Work</a>
                <a href="Rakibul%20Hasan%20Rizvi.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"
                        style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Resume</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get In Touch</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-graphic">
            <!-- Profile image inside the glowing blob shape -->
            <div class="blob">
                <img src="images/profile-removebg.png" alt="Rakibul Hasan Rizvi" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>